sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant API as Presentation API
    participant BL as Business Logic
    participant DB as Persistence Database

    User->>API: Complete review form
    Note over User, API: Requires user to be logged in
    API->>BL: Submit review data (API call)
    BL->>DB: Create review record
    DB-->>BL: Confirm review creation
    BL-->>API: Review stored and linked to place
    API-->>User: Show success message
